title: Add compliance language
author: ebullient
content:
[![🗳️ Vote progress](https://www.commonhaus.org/votes/commonhaus/foundation/274.svg)](https://github.com/commonhaus/foundation/pull/274#issuecomment-3225025075 "IC_kwDOKRPTI87AOfoz")

Clarification of CONTRIBUTING guidelines

voting group: @commonhaus/cf-council 

Do one of the following:

- React with 👍 (:+1:) or Approve a review  if it looks good to you
- React with 👀 (:eyes:) if you're "ok" with it (it may not be your favorite)
- If you think it needs discussion or revision:
    - Create a review, add your comments and require changes
    - Use the +- button to make a suggestion (instead of just adding a comment).
